ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
SubjectHenderson, The Hon. Paul J., RELOCATION EXPENSES additional
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. PAUL J. HENDERSON, who was required to relocate to London, Ontario, following his appointment as a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice of Ontario, Family Court, on October 29, 2010.
